Principal BEP 20 coin: mana 

The idea is to create a system which can mint mana tokens trough NFTs, and do so in a way that would not be hyperinflationary.

Example:
NFT - Mana source of the gods
Qualities...
Name: fountain of Thor
Mint rate: 50 mana/day
Duration: 20 days
Rarity level: 5

You can then use this mana to fight NPCs. NPCs can then drop different kinds of NFTs, including mana sources.
Most importantly, NPCs can drop fighting NFTs, which can be used to gain strength and to be able to beat stronger adversaries.
Stronger opponents have a greater chance of dropping a valuable item.

Fighting will happen once per day at most, since we don't wanna have millions of NFTs flodding the marketplace.
In order to achieve this, fighting NFTs will have stamina that would get drained once the fight happens.

Example:
NFT - Young elf apprentice
Level: 7
Stamina remaning: 100%
Fighting mana cost: 250
Rarity level: 27

(esto hay que verlo, no le veo mucho uso por ahora a las stats de pelea, pero tienen que tener exp o nivel que haga que
se pueda pelear con monstruos mejores, y stamina para no permitir que peleen todo el tiempo).

Otra opción es que el costo de pelea se duplique cada vez que se pelea, y recién se resetee a los días, como hace alpaca.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Burn mechanism:

Key for this to work is the limited time the fountains have. These will make good fighting PJs more valuable, since they will be the ones
running the game long term. And they will be seek to obtain more fountains.

Fighting mana cost:
We could have different mana cost for different characters, making the ones which low mana, the most valuable.
